description:
Oh, this is such a typical photo, but I just couldn't resist taking it. Everyone around me at the moment was people also trying to make this shot, and for a moment I felt incredible unity with them. This one is not particularly clear either, so I hope you can forgive me. 
The address is Hong Kong, Choi Hung Estate, by the way, besides the eponymous metro station. Just follow the signs in the MTR and enter inside the estate (there's no fence or guards), walk to the car park and take the stairs all the way up. You'll discover a basketball court up there, and then you'll realize you're staring at this beautiful view also. Hope this helps :)
